title: BMC Election 2017: What Celebrities Had To Say At The Voting Booth!
text: BMC Election 2017: What Celebrities Had To Say At The Voting Booth! By tweet The BMC Elections (2017) took place in Mumbai yesterday. Following their citizen duties, celebrities made sure to vote. They even spoke to the media, urging their fans and fellow citizens to fulfill their duties. Celebrities such as Ranveer Singh, Shah Rukh Khan, Sachin Tendulkar, Vivek Oberoi were spotted at the voting booth. Check out what celebrities had to say here : TAGS
